<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-6805640_enabled_by_UniProt_Q9Y243_R-HSA-6805640_controller_BFO_0000066_reaction_R-HSA-6805640_enabled_by_UniProt_Q9Y243_R-HSA-6805640_controller_location_lociGO_0005654_Reactome_R-HSA-6804758>
